title: Beautiful Creatures - Beautiful Creatures (2001)
description:
Beautiful Creatures - Beautiful Creatures (2001)


The things we don't even know that we don't know. For most
people, Beautiful Creatures is a great album they didn't even
know they didn't know. Of course, there is a loyal fan base
that knows. And after listening, you'll know what they know.

Beautiful Creatures has been described as "gritty, hard-
hitting post-grunge rock". I call it good old fashioned
corn-fed rock-n-roll.

Enjoy.
